C-x C-s to save

C-x C-w to write to a file (sace as)

C-x u to undo

C-s to search. Searches forward

C-r to search. Searches backwards

C-r/s to go to next search result (wording)

M-x goto-line to go to a specific line

C-space to set mark. Move using arrow keys or keys described on lines 5 - 12

C/M-w cut/copy as the selected section

C-y to paste (yank, Jim is a yanker)

C-x i to insert another file

C-x 4 b <name>  open another buffer called 'name' in another window

C-x 5 b <name> open another buffer called 'name' in another frame

C-x C-b to list existing buffers

C-x o to move between windows

C-x 0 to delete window

M- </> go to start/end of buffer